(44, 19, 22, 44, 13, 5, 5, 'ministered unto him', 'Ministers in Mission', 'Both passages emphasize the role of ministers in spreading the word of God. In Acts 19:22, Timotheus and Erastus are sent to assist Paul, paralleling how John serves as a minister in Acts 13:5.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
